      <abstract>
        <p>True North Communications acquires Howard, Merrell &amp; Partners (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>True North Communications in Chicago said yesterday that it had acquired Howard, Merrell &amp; Partners in Raleigh, N.C. Terms were not disclosed.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>True North Communications in Chicago said yesterday that it had acquired Howard, Merrell &amp; Partners in Raleigh, N.C. Terms were not disclosed.</p>
        <p>Howard, Merrell, with 80 employees and billings estimated at $90 million from clients like BB&amp;T and Kimberly-Clark, will operate as an autonomous unit of the Bozell Group unit of True North. Mac Merrell, 58, continues as chief executive.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
